  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Community Reconciliation and Strengthening of Living Together in Central Mali</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Given the increase in violence in Mali, this project supports immediate measures that focus on sustainable intra- and inter-community dialogue around common peacebuilding interests in the country, while promoting community reconciliation and joint socio-economic initiatives that promote the prospects of living together peacefully. Further, this project also aims to respond to the impact of COVID-19 on vulnerable communities through conducting activities to mitigate the spread of the pandemic in areas with a high concentration of IDPs. Emphasis has been placed on strengthening the strategy for raising awareness among displacement affected populations, as well as at the level of health checkpoints.</narrative>
  </description>
